name: HIBRIDISM014
description: WEBART with audio. Developed through the programs Rhinoceros 3D and 3ds Max. Cooperative combination between the synthetic and nature. The dichotomous clash ends in this 0:14 second narrative, creating a unified point of view; where technology and nature merge biologically, giving bith to a third being, who lives and co-creates other alternatives.  https://homeostasislab.org/visualizar/obra/2260  http://k0k0n.bandcamp.com  http://k0k0n.tumblr.com
